| applyRawBrightness(...)Calling setBrightness() or directly setting screenBrightness forces a fixed screen brightness, bypassing Android's adaptive brightness feature (introduced in Android 9) which adjusts brightness based on ambient light to improve battery life. |
| applyScreenBrightness(...)Calling setBrightness() or directly setting screenBrightness forces a fixed screen brightness, bypassing Android's adaptive brightness feature (introduced in Android 9) which adjusts brightness based on ambient light to improve battery life. |
| setBrightness(...)Calling setBrightness() or directly setting screenBrightness forces a fixed screen brightness, bypassing Android's adaptive brightness feature (introduced in Android 9) which adjusts brightness based on ambient light to improve battery life. |
